         <abstract audience="internal" id="aspace_aa5cca4a7317dcc4f57f41c5184e30db">The Bettie Hiter Willis Papers, 1864-1942, is comprised of digitized diary entries and letters from Willis, including documents created during the Civil War.</abstract>
